# Comprehensive Nagatoro Novel Game Script
# This script contains multiple interconnected dialogues with backgrounds and functions
name: OpeningScene
Start
Show Background beachBackground
Nagatoro says Welcome to our story! I hope you enjoy this adventure.
Player says Hi Nagatoro! What are we going to do today?
Nagatoro says Let's explore the beach first, then maybe go to the classroom later.
Wait 2 seconds
Nagatoro says The weather is perfect for a walk along the shore!
Player says Yes, the view is beautiful here.
call beachActivity
Jump To BeachExploration

function beachActivity
Nagatoro says Look at all these seashells! Want to collect some?
Player says Sure, that sounds fun!
Nagatoro says I found a really pretty pink one!
Wait 1 seconds
Nagatoro says Oh, and there's a starfish too!
end

---

name: BeachExploration
Start
Show Background beachBackground
Nagatoro says Did you enjoy our time at the beach?
Player says Very much! The ocean is so calming.
Nagatoro says I love coming here when I need to think.
Wait 3 seconds
Nagatoro says But now, let's head to the classroom. I have something special planned!
Player says What do you have planned?
Nagatoro says You'll see! Follow me!
Jump To ClassroomArrival

---

name: ClassroomArrival
Start
Show Background classBackground
Nagatoro says Here we are! The classroom is quiet today.
Player says It's different from being outside, more intimate somehow.
Nagatoro says That's exactly what I was thinking!
Wait 1 seconds
Show Nagatoro with emotion Naga_Lean_Bikini_Sidelook_CatOpen
Nagatoro says I prepared some tea for us.
Player says You're so thoughtful, Nagatoro.
call classroomActivity
Jump To TeaTime

function classroomActivity
Nagatoro says Sit down, make yourself comfortable.
Player says Thanks, this chair is really cozy.
Wait 2 seconds
Nagatoro says I've been working on a surprise for you.
Player says Really? What kind of surprise?
Nagatoro says You'll have to wait and see!
end

---

name: TeaTime
Start
Show Background classBackground
Nagatoro says Here's your tea. I hope you like it.
Player says It smells wonderful! What's in it?
Nagatoro says Just a special blend I found. It helps you relax.
Wait 2 seconds
Player says Mmm, it's delicious. You really know your teas!
Nagatoro says I've had practice making tea for my friends.
Player says You're always so caring.
Nagatoro says That's what friends do for each other.
call teaConversation
Jump To StudyTime

function teaConversation
Player says So, what do you usually do in this classroom?
Nagatoro says I like to read books and work on art projects here.
Wait 1 seconds
Player says Art projects? That sounds interesting.
Nagatoro says Yes! I love drawing and painting in my free time.
Player says I'd love to see your artwork sometime.
Nagatoro says Maybe I'll show you some next time we meet!
end

---

name: StudyTime
Start
Show Background classBackground
Nagatoro says Would you like to study together?
Player says Sure! What subject were you thinking?
Nagatoro says How about literature? I brought some interesting books.
Wait 1 seconds
Show Nagatoro with emotion Naga_Lean_Bikini_Sidelook_CatClosed
Nagatoro says I especially like romantic stories.
Player says Really? That's sweet of you to share.
Nagatoro says There's something special about sharing stories with friends.
Player says I agree. Stories bring people together.
call studyBreak
Jump To SunsetView

function studyBreak
Wait 3 seconds
Nagatoro says I think we deserve a break from studying.
Player says Good idea. My brain was starting to feel full.
Nagatoro says How about we look out the window for a moment?
Player says The view is beautiful, especially during sunset.
end

---

name: SunsetView
Start
Show Background classBackground
Nagatoro says Look at the sunset! The sky is turning orange and pink.
Player says It's breathtaking! The colors are so vibrant.
Nagatoro says This is one of my favorite times of day.
Wait 4 seconds
Player says The light streaming through the window is so warm.
Nagatoro says It makes everything look magical, doesn't it?
Jump To BeachMemory

---

name: BeachMemory
Start
Show Background beachBackground
# Flashback to the beach
Nagatoro says Remember when we were at the beach earlier?
Player says Yes, it feels like just now, but also like a long time ago.
Nagatoro says Time moves differently when you're having fun.
Wait 2 seconds
Nagatoro says I'm glad we got to spend this time together today.
Player says Me too, Nagatoro. These moments mean a lot to me.
Nagatoro says That makes me happy to hear.
Jump To ClassroomMemory

---

name: ClassroomMemory
Start
Show Background classBackground
# Back in the classroom
Nagatoro says Our time in the classroom was nice too.
Player says Yes, the contrast between the open beach and cozy classroom was perfect.
Nagatoro says I planned it that way intentionally.
Wait 1 seconds
Player says You really thought this through, didn't you?
Nagatoro says Every detail matters when I'm with someone special.
Player says That's really touching, Nagatoro.
call finalWords
Jump To ClosingScene

function finalWords
Nagatoro says Before you go, I want you to know something.
Player says What is it?
Wait 2 seconds
Nagatoro says You make these ordinary moments feel extraordinary.
Player says Nagatoro...
Nagatoro says Thank you for spending today with me.
end

---

name: ClosingScene
Start
Show Background beachBackground
# Final scene back at the beach as the day ends
Nagatoro says As the day comes to an end, I feel content.
Player says Today was perfect. Thank you for everything, Nagatoro.
Nagatoro says The pleasure was all mine.
Wait 3 seconds
Show Nagatoro with emotion Naga_Lean_Bikini_Sidelook_CatOpen
Nagatoro says I hope we can do this again soon.
Player says I'd like that very much.
Nagatoro says Until next time, take care!
Wait 2 seconds
Player says Goodbye, Nagatoro. See you soon!
Hide Nagatoro
Clear Background
End